a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirimdhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43173,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/16\/concession-women-to-lower\/","url_meta":{"origin":15161,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Clothing: Concession for women to lower garments","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever trails their garment in pride, Allah will never look at them on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Umm Salamah said, \u201cWhat should women do with their hems?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSlacken them by a handspan.\u201d She\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43004,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/10\/prefer-white-garments\/","url_meta":{"origin":15161,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Clothes: Prefer white garments, living or deceased","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 10, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cClothe yourselves in white garments, for they are the best of garments, and shroud your deceased in them.\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe most beloved to me is to shroud oneself\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;